bs-contextmenu-desc: Forni menus contextual pro varie ligamines
bs-contextmenu-pref-modus: Aperir menu contextual per (non pro mobile):
bs-contextmenu-pref-modus-just-right-mou: Clicca sur le button dextre del mouse (premer CTRL monstrara le menu contextual normal del navigator)
bs-contextmenu-pref-modus-ctrl-and-right: Clicca sur le button dextre del mouse durante que tu preme CTRL (un clic dextre normal monstrara le menu contextual normal del navigator)
bs-contextmenu-media-view-page: Vider pagina de description del file e historia del file
bs-contextmenu-user-talk: Lassar message in pagina de discussion
